I have enough context to write the verifier. The contract is going in as a minimal no-import Foundry target: zero-arg constructor, direct-use JUICE staking with an extreme `stakeWeek`, dynamic profit accounting in JUICE, and explicit reverts only for concrete preconditions like “staking not open”, “no verifier-held JUICE”, or “reward has not accrued yet”.
